{"tid":601487,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本流行女星自曝玩《怪物獵人：世界》400多小時現場演示輕鬆討伐滅盡龍","createTime":"2018-03-22T09:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T09:59:20.000Z","uid":49391,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e94cb958582fe2e9defec5d045253bbfe032db45","tid":601487,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T09:09:10.000Z","msg":"日本流行樂團Morning Musume的前成員後藤真希是《怪物獵人》的超級粉絲，曾經也為《怪物獵人：攜帶版3》拍攝廣告。她表示自己玩《怪物獵人：世界》已經有400到500小時。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6tqz2bhD_aM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6tqz2bhD_aM&d=jYQxgPNCiBBMWRoR2vEy0BFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=6dd9a2b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6tqz2bhD_aM</a><br />\n<br />\n在最近的《怪物獵人：世界》活動中，後藤真希被問到玩《怪物獵人》系列的總時長大概是多少，她回答說大概已經超過五六千小時了，而她實際的《怪物獵人》遊戲時長已經達到了7000小時以上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/03/20180321_gtz_412_9/gamersky_02small_04_2018321211979A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F03%2F20180321_gtz_412_9%2Fgamersky_02small_04_2018321211979A.jpg&h=75273ee8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後藤真希還在現場為我們演示瞭如何討伐滅盡龍，一通操作行雲流水，老獵人認證完畢。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/03/20180321_gtz_412_9/gamersky_01small_02_2018321211925F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F03%2F20180321_gtz_412_9%2Fgamersky_01small_02_2018321211925F.jpg&h=811d44a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad0bfe1dc1143b93f20c8852ce3cf6b5216ea743","tid":601487,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T09:15:10.000Z","msg":"得罪講句,女人就應該用弓/弩/笛,響後方支援,等男人上前線"},{"pid":"1ca3847fe404b59908754279961cfb1ae1b90203","tid":601487,"uid":3748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T09:43:14.000Z","msg":"好想睇多次佢著喪服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8070269a490abb15a7c03e899ada033218c09e","tid":601487,"uid":135